{"type": "article", "id": 51354, "title": "混凝土和玻璃制作的灯具，创造轻盈和厚重的反差感｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-03-21T22:53:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 48629, "name": "Elago"}, {"id": 48630, "name": "Bandido Studio"}, {"id": 48631, "name": "Carl Hansen & Søn"}, {"id": 48632, "name": "Mauricio Ercoli"}, {"id": 6594, "name": "Karim Rashid"}, {"id": 48633, "name": "Helena Jonasson"}, {"id": 48634, "name": "Veronica Dagnert"}, {"id": 48635, "name": "Cesar Núñez"}, {"id": 37273, "name": "Brad Ascalon"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 110, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180321195140zHqN7IMS2mDVcUkg.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s5 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Preludia Collection by Carl Hansen &amp; Søn</h3><p>丹麦高级家具制造商 Carl Hansen &amp; Søn 与美国设计师 Brad Ascalon 合作，推出 Preludia 系列桌椅。这个系列最初是在斯德哥尔摩家具展上推出的。</p><p>Preludia 系列延续了 Carl Hansen &amp; Søn 110 年以来的现代简约风格，又激发起设计师进一步探索木材潜力的兴趣。全木制作的 Preludia 桌椅，亦有钢质椅腿和雪橇式底座的选择。酒吧椅也是实木框架，搭配层压桌面和铸铝细节，以保证椅子的耐用性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195226FPz3DBJvXAch7qTS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.724939\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195226Ru6n9j8MUvr7XBIb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.524450\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195227bMw1TBigR08APZqG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.778729\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195226LQRtrbznEw0MYHpi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.953545\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195228LAkWVNtpXYcwl39z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195229KM40mdGoWTXbuhif.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/carl-hansen-and-son-brad-ascalon-preludia-series-03-20-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>BO Lamp by Bandido Studio &amp;  Cesar Núñez</h3><p>墨西哥 Bandido 工作室与设计师 Cesar Núñez 合作制作了这款名为 BO 的台灯，一个圆柱形的底座，顶部的斜剖面是光源所在处，被一个 V 形折叠金属片包裹，使得光源不会直射出来，而是照在金属片上折射出温暖而柔和的光线。</p><p>Bandido 团队表示：“灵感来源于一个反复的过程，其中包括观察光是如何被自然变换的，它如何反射并被不同的元素吸收。”</p><p>此外，隐藏在圆柱形底座中的触摸式传感器还允许用户改变 LED 灯的强度，用以调节空间氛围。提供香槟白、牛津灰以及玫瑰桃粉色三种选择。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195445DkTZfvKdumwNqb2o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195446HkjFtJ23CXwAQ9hr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803211954462y3vqZDshUHLaEgY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195447Eg3dmxVFOCGjpkHe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/03/20/bo-lamp-bandido-studio-cesar-nunez-design-mexico/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Cast Lights by Helena Jonasson &amp; Veronica Dagnert</h3><p>Modern Design Review 杂志与 Ace Hotel 伦敦 Shoreditch 店合作，找来一组设计师来为酒店内设计酒店定制款物品。在整个 Ready Made Go 系列中，这个名为 Cast 的灯具系列挺有意思，出自伦敦工作室 studio vit 之手。</p><p>设计师 Helena Jonasson 和 Veronica Dagnert 的作品大多呈现出极简主义的特征，但设计师认为她们最看重的是以功能性为基础的简约造型。</p><p>Cast 灯具由铸造混凝土和手工吹制的硼硅酸盐玻璃制成，分为吊灯款和台灯款。两款都是由基本的几何形状组成，强化了两种材料轻盈与厚重的反差感，还运用重力法则，制造了某种紧张感。售价 263 欧元起，<a href=\"http://www.petitefriture.com/fre/33/cast\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803211955381SQjmrawpP9gsMux.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195537rLRpuioKzfM1cqVv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195538hB7y5boEcAJmID9p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195538qR9XghEHxKSsoDMl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195539fQqslhoIwO2GULT3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803211955397a04IHT8t9NPUDMC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Koop Chair by Karim Rashid</h3><p>以艺术风格闻名世界的纽约设计师 Karim Rashid 为芬兰家具品牌 Martela 设计了 Koop 椅。 蛋形椅的形状造出一个舒适的半开放式的阅读空间，也可以抱个笔记本电脑蜷在里面工作或是打电话。设计师声称，用户愿意的话，也可以睡在这把椅子上。</p><p>Koop 椅的结构采用隐藏式旋转底座，由玻璃纤维涂层制成，可提供包括白色、绿色、浅蓝色、紫色以及金属灰色在内的不少颜色，并配有柔软的软垫内饰。它圆润的形状也是意在跟充满直线和角度的建筑空间产生碰撞。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195608YLanT73bAOwzBdqr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195608d3CXS8nfMpuhL5qs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018032119560810tE3awjfIXSrF8R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195608RD2NYyVAoHqEh71a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803211956087IXVkEym05ZnzPeB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Turk Head Stool by Mauricio Ercoli</h3><p>设计师 Mauricio Ercoli 的新作是一把名为 Turk Head 的凳子。从名字不难看出，这把凳子与土耳其的联系。据设计师描述，其灵感源自土耳其人用作装饰的头结。多股线交织在一起形成闭合回路，仿佛扣在凳子底座上一般，看起来就像是个头重脚轻的家伙。</p><p>简单的原木底座由三条支撑腿组成。这个凳面充满艺术性，但其功能性也不差，加强了这款紧凑简单的凳子的舒适性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195658MFcZkC7ie40YWKHr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.356190\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195659voYNm04jTOE6aFVn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803211957004BJ8ga9E1vmktwdj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.341905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195700ZEpwh2l8DRH41voY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.496190\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/03/21/a-stool-with-a-headdress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>AirPods Leather Case by Elago</h3><p>加州设计公司 Elago 推出了这款 AirPods 黄铜天然牛皮革保护皮套，很复古。独特的皮革设计，将AirPods 融合至经典的保护皮套，使用黄铜材质的扣环，不易生锈，延长使用寿命。下方开孔设计可以直接充电，即使在充电时，也提供完整的保护。复古的金色铜质扣环，可随意扣在行李箱、背包等地方。售价 19.99 美元，<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/elago-AirPods-Leather-Case-Brown/dp/B073GM45W1/ref=sr_1_13?tag=yankodesign05-20&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1521583808&amp;sr=8-13&amp;keywords=elago+airpods\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买。</a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195737iAnYKZyoVJ5use0k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769524\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195737BcztN3Y6lTI5HufF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195737gaUuW50CVn3k6Hfi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195738B645dahfVEywZkgP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195738AYG2ORqgSrKWvz7a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180321195739EPqGvg71XWBJpdaS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}